//   • pi — vendor brand mark (Inflection; trademark of its owner, used only to identify the
//     running agent), matching the mark in the referenced Skillz app.
// Agents without a mark here (hermes, aider, generic) fall back to a tinted two-letter
// monogram. Hermes's official mark is a detailed portrait that turns to mush at icon size,
// so it intentionally uses the monogram instead of a vector silhouette.
// Do not hand-edit path data — regenerate from the source SVGs.
